data.description: Welcome to this adorable home in the highly sought-after China Spring Independent School District. This stunning home offers a harmonious blend of elegance and modern upgrades, providing a luxurious and comfortable living experience. Boasting 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths. Designed with the perfect layout, the inviting entryway opens into the spacious living area with an open dining area connected to the spacious kitchen. Enjoy preparing meals and spending time together gathered around the kitchen island. The isolated primary bedroom includes a large walk-in closet and a relaxing spa-like bathroom.  Another appealing aspect of this property is the absence of a homeowners' association (HOA). This means you can enjoy the freedom and flexibility to personalize and utilize your property without the restrictions typically associated with HOAs. Embrace your creativity and make this house truly feel like home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your own. Easy access to China Spring Rd for a quick shopping, dining, and entertainment commute.  Right down the road from the Waco Airport, Lake Waco, and the Lake Waco Golf Club, A new roof was installed in August of 2023. See this beautiful home before it's gone! Such a great location! This lovely home is ready for its next owner.
